
# John 3:16 (New American Bible (Revised Edition))
16 For God so loved the world that he gave[^a] his only Son, so that everyone who believes in him might not perish but might have eternal life.[^A]

### Footnotes
[^a]: 3:16 <b class="catch-word">Gave**: as a gift in the incarnation, and also “over to death” in the crucifixion; cf. [Rom 8:32].

### Crossrefs
[^A]: 1 Jn 4:9.

